---
import './Foundations.css';
import SectionLabel from '../../../../components/SectionLabel';

// 02 — Foundations. The three principles the system is built on.
---

<section id="foundations" class="band" aria-labelledby="foundations-label">
  <div class="wrap">
    <SectionLabel index="02" label="Foundations" id="foundations-label" />
    <div class="principles">
      <article class="principle" data-reveal>
        <h3 class="t-heading">Access is the floor</h3>
        <p class="t-body principle__copy">We start from the people most easily left out &mdash; readable type, generous contrast, motion that switches off, focus you can always see. Set the floor high and everyone rises with it.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="principle" data-reveal style="--reveal-delay: 80ms">
        <h3 class="t-heading">The work goes unseen</h3>
        <p class="t-body principle__copy">Like the character we are named for, the system holds the page together without being noticed. Space does the structuring; a hairline shows only where it earns its place.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="principle" data-reveal style="--reveal-delay: 160ms">
        <h3 class="t-heading">One system, every surface</h3>
        <p class="t-body principle__copy">Two families, one accent and a single set of tokens carry everything from the address bar to the share card. Change a token, and the whole brand moves with it.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
